<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 06:19:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国机器人大会聚焦类人机器人的变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-robots-conference-spotlights-changing-face-humanoids-2024-08-26/</link><description>随着中国寻求在人形机器人开发方面取得领先，其供应链在北京举行的世界机器人大会上展示了更便宜和创新的零部件，但一些高管警告称，该行业尚未提高产品可靠性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 06:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-robots-conference-spotlights-changing-face-humanoids-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>印度黄金关税下调可能引发节日期间的购买热潮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-gold-duty-cut-likely-spark-buying-spree-during-festivals-2024-08-26/</link><description>行业官员表示，即将到来的节日期间，印度的黄金需求可能会保持强劲，因为进口关税的大幅降低使价格具有吸引力，为零售消费者带来安慰并鼓励购买。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 05:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-gold-duty-cut-likely-spark-buying-spree-during-festivals-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国工业界寻求缓解拜登-哈里斯对中国关税的大幅上调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-industry-seeks-easing-steep-biden-harris-china-tariff-hikes-2024-08-26/</link><description>拜登-哈里斯政府预计将于本周宣布对某些中国进口商品大幅提高关税的最终实施计划，如果美国工业如愿，许多计划中的关税将得到软化。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 05:07:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-industry-seeks-easing-steep-biden-harris-china-tariff-hikes-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>全球前景黯淡，央行转向预示着更多动荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/darkening-global-outlook-central-bank-pivots-signal-more-turbulence-2024-08-26/</link><description>越来越多的增长乏力和就业市场风险的迹象给出席美联储杰克逊霍尔年度会议的全球政策制定者蒙上了阴影，凸显了随着美国和欧洲央行考虑降息，货币政策轨迹正在发生变化。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 05:03:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/darkening-global-outlook-central-bank-pivots-signal-more-turbulence-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>所向披靡的德约科维奇在纽约揭幕战面临阿尔伯特考验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/all-conquering-djokovic-faces-albot-test-new-york-opener-2024-08-26/</link><description>美国网球公开赛第一轮将于周一开始，世界顶尖选手将在纽约争夺大满贯的荣耀。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 04:59:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/all-conquering-djokovic-faces-albot-test-new-york-opener-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：鲍威尔看跌期权让市场放心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-26/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 04:32:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国在南海的举动“具有侵略性、不专业且非法”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-actions-south-china-sea-patently-illegal-philippine-defence-min-says-2024-08-26/</link><description>过去一周发生一系列空中和海上冲突和事件后，菲律宾政府周一谴责中国在南海“一再采取侵略性、不专业和非法的”行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 02:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-actions-south-china-sea-patently-illegal-philippine-defence-min-says-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国军队将在中缅边境举行武装巡逻和实弹演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-says-it-conducted-armed-patrols-joint-police-patrols-near-china-2024-08-26/</link><description>中国军方周一表示，随着缅甸执政军政府和叛军之间的战斗升级，中国军方已在中缅边境附近组织军队和空地警察联合巡逻，以维护安全稳定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:43:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-says-it-conducted-armed-patrols-joint-police-patrols-near-china-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市犹豫不决，美元下跌；石油收益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-26/</link><description>周一亚洲主要股市变得犹豫不决，而美元和债券收益率在通胀数据公布之前下跌，投资者希望通胀数据将为美国和欧洲降息铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>尽管努力重建信任，中国与菲律宾在南海仍发生冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-clash-south-china-sea-despite-efforts-rebuild-trust-2024-08-25/</link><description>周日，菲律宾和中国在南中国海有争议的海域发生冲突，马尼拉称这是一次为渔民执行补给任务，这是该战略航道上一系列海空对抗中的最新一起。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 10:33:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-clash-south-china-sea-despite-efforts-rebuild-trust-2024-08-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行行长刘金辞职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bank-china-president-liu-resigns-chairman-be-acting-president-2024-08-25/</link><description>中国银行表示，副董事长兼行长刘进因个人原因辞职，自周日起生效。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:52:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bank-china-president-liu-resigns-chairman-be-acting-president-2024-08-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国称对南海菲律宾船只采取“管控措施”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-took-control-measures-against-philippine-vessel-south-china-sea-2024-08-25/</link><description>中国周日表示，已对南海的一艘菲律宾船只采取“控制措施”，两国在南海争议海域的对抗不断升级。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 07:51:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-took-control-measures-against-philippine-vessel-south-china-sea-2024-08-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责美国将企业列入出口管制名单，誓言采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-slams-us-adding-firms-export-control-list-vows-action-2024-08-25/</link><description>周五，美国将 105 家俄罗斯和中国公司列入贸易限制名单，原因是它们涉嫌支持俄罗斯军方。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 04:47:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-slams-us-adding-firms-export-control-list-vows-action-2024-08-25/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称中国根据市场原则监管债券市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-regulates-bond-market-based-market-principles-state-media-says-2024-08-24/</link><description>官方媒体周六表示，中国金融监管机构根据市场原则、宏观审慎和合规角度对债券市场进行监管，否认了干预市场的说法。</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 03:48:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-regulates-bond-market-based-market-principles-state-media-says-2024-08-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾敦促中国在耀斑事件后停止“挑衅”行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-urges-china-halt-provocative-dangerous-actions-after-flare-incidents-2024-08-24/</link><description>菲律宾周六呼吁北京“立即停止一切挑衅和危险行动”，此前菲律宾指责北京8月22日一架马尼拉飞机在巡逻时“无理”地从中国占领的渚碧礁部署照明弹。</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 02:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-urges-china-halt-provocative-dangerous-actions-after-flare-incidents-2024-08-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>